==Trivia==
*In the comics, Danny Rand is [[Luke Cage]]'s best friend and the two of them founded "[[w:c:marvel:Heroes for Hire|Heroes for Hire]]", a superhero protection agency.
*Danny Rand is shown to be a fan of hip hop music, including [[Dr. Dre]], [[Outkast]], [[Camp Lo]], [[Killah Priest]], [[The Cool Kids]] and [[Anderson .Paak]].
*In ''[[The Defenders]]'' episode ''[[The Defenders (episode)|The Defenders]]'', [[Jessica Jones]] calls Rand "[[Ironclad]]" instead of Iron Fist. In the comics, Ironclad is the alias for Michael Steel. Ironclad also appeared in the non-canon video game ''[[The Incredible Hulk (video game)|The Incredible Hulk]]''.

==Behind the Scenes==
*Prior to the casting of [[Finn Jones]], many people expressed hope that the main role would be portrayed by an actor of Chinese or East Asian descent even though the comic book character was Caucasian. When the Caucasian actor was cast, the decision was criticized by, among others, Marvel writer {{WPS|Marjorie Liu}}<ref name="Liu">[http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/iron-fist-marvel-writer-outraged-over-games-of-thrones-actor-finn-jones-casting-in-netflix-show-a6903601.html : Marvel writer outraged over Games of Thrones actor Finn Jones casting in Netflix show]</ref> and actress [[Chloe Bennet]].<ref name="Bennett">[http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/04/05/agents-of-shield-s-chloe-bennet-why-movies-and-marvel-need-to-diversify.html Agents of SHIELD’s Chloe Bennet: Why I Stopped Using My Chinese Last Name]</ref>
*Before the casting of Finn Jones, many martial arts actors were considered for the role of Iron Fist:
**{{WPS|Ray Park}} was considered for the role during the early 2000s after he portrayed [[Toad|Mortimer Toynbee/Toad]] in the {{WPS|X-Men (film series)|''X-Men'' movie series}}.
**[[Scott Adkins]] was considered for the role of Iron Fist as well as the [[Punisher]] in the late 2000s following his stunt doubling of [[Ryan Reynolds]] as [[Deadpool|Wade Wilson/Deadpool]] in 2009. He later played [[Lucian Aster]] in ''[[Doctor Strange (film)|Doctor Strange]]''.
**[[Lewis Tan]], who played [[Shatterstar|Rusty/Shatterstar]] in ''{{WPS|Deadpool 2}}'' almost auditioned for the role as well.
*[[David Armstrong]] and [[Jared Burke]] were stunt doubles for [[Finn Jones]] in the role of Iron Fist.
*[[Rocky Kellon Smith]] was a stand-in for [[Finn Jones]] in the role of Iron Fist.
*In the Latin American Spanish dub of ''[[The Defenders (episode)|The Defenders]]'', when [[Jessica Jones]] calls him incorrectly Ironclad, she calls him [[Iron Man]].

